channel.title: [PI] Custom Donator Tags Cannot Find Symbol Help
channel.description:
I followed a Tutorial over at Rune Serv about custom donator tags on project insanity, for one he tells me to edit the playersaving.java but the stuff im supposed to find is in playersave.java, also when i compile i get this Error, and by the way i didnt put it in player saving i put in playersave
[code]src\server\model\players\packets\Commands.java:139: cannot find symbol symbol : method getYelltag() location: class server.model.players.Client c.getYelltag(); ^[/code]

item.title: [PI] Custom Donator Tags Cannot Find Symbol Help
item.dc:creator: @ExtremeX-Scape Ryley
item.description:
@ExtremeX-Scape wrote:

^Wtf, are you talking about?

@OP You need to add the method if you don’t have it, or you need to capitalize the ‘T’
for ‘tag’, Java is case sensitive.
